data.value: QR Mate is your go-to solution for generating QR codes with ease and efficiency. Whether you need to create QR codes for asset management or any other data-gathering purpose, QR Mate simplifies the process with its user-friendly interface and versatile options. It keeps track of all your creations with the built-in history feature (Log). With QR Mate, you can generate and manage QR codes quickly, securely, and conveniently.
